data.description:
This property is eligible as an assumable loan. Feel free to ask the listing agent for more information. Come take a look at this lovely property at Overland Grove in Forney. This home is conveniently located between Highway 80 and I-20. This beautiful neighborhood has a ton of amenities. 

Here are some of the features:
Oversized windows - lots of natural light.
Open space kitchen.
Unique Backyard view!
Split floor plan layout.
Under the cabinet lighting.
Marble accented fireplace.
Stainless steel GE appliances.
Covered patio with float shelving.
High ceilings.
Stunning entry with long hallway.
Solar energy!

Neighborhood amenities - state of the art clubhouse, Lounging area outdoor with tvs & grill, “The Dock”, playground, fantastic swimming pool, “The Garden”

Downtown Forney nearby featuring locally owned cafes and boutique stores.
